        How to Make a Complaint About a Real Estate Agent in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Most Queensland sales proceed without significant issues. But when an agent fails to act in your best interest, you need to know your options and how to use them.
      </p>
    </div>
